-if he will make a statement.
-[79468]</p><p><a name="06062734000043"><b><a name="06062734000088">Barry
-Gardiner</b><i> [holding answer 26 June 2006]:</i> A reply was
-sent to the hon. Member on 22
-June.</p><p><a name="06062734000044">The Department
