-Hospitality</h3><p><a name="06062734000048"><b><a name="06062734000091">David
-Simpson:</b> To ask the Secretary of State for
-Environment, Food and Rural Affairs if he will keep a separate record
-of the amount spent annually by his Department on alcohol for
